'''飓风贡萨洛'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Gonzalo}}）是一场强劲的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]，于2014年10月对[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]和[[百慕大|百慕大]]构成灾难性破坏。贡萨洛是繼[[2010年大西洋飓风季|2010年]]的[[飓风伊戈尔|飓风伊戈尔]]后最强烈的[[大西洋飓风季|大西洋飓风]]<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | date = 2015-05-07 | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150510121046/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-050515.txt | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-050515.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archivedate = 2015-05-10}}</ref>，在[[飓风费伊_(2014年)|飓风费伊]]偷袭百慕大不到一周后袭击该岛，2014年由此成为有纪录以来百慕大首次在一年中遭受两场飓风袭击。系统于10月12日经[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]以东的一股[[东风波|东风波]]发展形成，先以[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风强度登陆[[安地卡岛|安地卡岛]]、[[圣马丁岛_(加勒比海)|圣马丁岛]]和[[安圭拉|安圭拉]]，并对邻近多个岛屿构成破坏。[[安提瓜和巴布达|安提瓜和巴布达]]遭受了4000万美元损失，背面群岛北部有大量船只严重受损或被毁。圣马丁和[[圣巴泰勒米|圣巴泰勒米]]有3人因风暴丧生。气旋向西北方向移动并增强成四级飓风，成为自[[2011年大西洋飓风季|2011年]]的[[2011年飓风奥菲莉亚|飓风奥菲莉亚]]以来大西洋上空形成的第一场大型飓风{{#tag:ref|大型飓风指[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]可以在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]中达到三级或以上的风暴<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}。接下来飓风结构和强度虽因[[眼墙置换|眼墙置换]]产生波动，但贡萨洛还是于10月16日达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时230公里的最高强度{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有风速数据均为1分钟持续风速。|group="注"}}。

百慕大在贡萨洛来袭数天前刚因飓风费伊导致大规模停电，岛上居民不得不仓促进行防灾准备。银行、商户、学校和政府办事处在风暴袭击前关闭，[[英国皇家海军|英国皇家海军]]“阿盖尔号”护卫舰从加勒比赶往百慕大提供紧急援助。气旋逐渐减弱，于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]10月18日凌晨0点30分以二级飓风强度直接登陆该岛，岛上受到时速高达232公里的阵风摧残，成百上千的树木倒塌，大量屋顶受损。风暴期间，全岛3.6万电力用户中有约3.1万失去供电，直至11月上旬才完全恢复。许多道路在飓风过后无法通行，很多地方已无法分清破坏是由贡萨洛还是费伊导致。百慕大团的军人与阿盖尔号船员承担了岛上部分早期清理和修复工作，据初步评估，风暴导致的破坏程度还不足以和[[2003年大西洋飓风季|2003年]]的[[飓风法比安|飓风法比安]]相提并论。灾害模拟公司估计，百慕大遭受的损失总额高达4亿美元，破坏程度虽大，但岛上没有出现人员丧生或重伤。

离开百慕大后，飓风加速向北大西洋水域前进，经过[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]东南近海后于10月19日转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。[[阿瓦隆半岛|阿瓦隆半岛]]东南部因阵风和暴雨引发停电和轻度洪灾。贡萨洛的残留形成新的天气系统，于10月21日袭击[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]和中欧，造成英国3人遇难，交通受严重影响。系统之后还在[[巴尔干半岛|巴尔干半岛]]上空引发倾盆大雨，导致[[希腊|希腊]]和[[保加利亚|保加利亚]]爆发严重洪灾。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Gonzalo 2014 track.png}}
10月4日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]{{#tag:ref|[[东风波|东风波]]指的是沿[[信风|信风]]移动的[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}离开西非海岸进入大西洋。虽然云系和[[雷暴|雷暴]]都有发展，但系统受到[[冷心低压|上层低压槽]]的不利影响，无法得到显著发展。10月10日，系统在接触向东传播的[[开尔文波|开尔文波]]后发展出更为集中的[[对流|对流]]。外界环境渐趋有利，[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]的结构逐渐改善，到10月11日已形成小规模[[低气压|低气压区]]。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]10月12日凌晨0点，[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]以东约630公里海域有热带低气压形成{{#tag:ref|根据美国国家飓风中心的定义，热带低气压是指[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]在每小时62公里以下的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}，并因[[风切变|风切变]]少，[[海面温度|水温]]较高而在12小时后强化成热带风暴贡萨洛。{{#tag:ref|根据美国国家飓风中心的定义，热带风暴是指持续风速在每小时63至118公里之间的热带气旋<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}<ref name="tcr">{{cite web | author = Daniel P. Brown | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Tropical Cyclone Report | date = 2015-03-04 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150403111044/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL082014_Gonzalo.pdf | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL082014_Gonzalo.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-04-03}}</ref>不过从当时的实际操作来看，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]是在飞入气旋的[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]][[侦察机|侦察机]]测得[[最大持续风速|地面风速]]达到每小时65公里后才于10月12日中午才开始针对气旋发布公告<ref name="disc1">{{cite web | author = Stacy R. Stewart | date = 2014-10-12 | title = Tropical Storm Gonzalo Special Discussion Number 1 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.001.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705124425/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-05}}</ref>。

[[File:Gonzalo_Oct_13_2014_1710Z.jpg|thumb]]
受大西洋中部上空的强烈[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，风暴转朝西面的[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]逼近<ref name="tcr" />。中心附件有强烈的雷暴活动，但组织结构起初较为混乱，并且也不对称<ref>{{cite web | author = Michael J. Brennan | date = 2014-10-12 | title = Tropical Storm Gonzalo Discussion Number 3 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.003.shtml | archivedate = 2015-07-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705150645/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no}}</ref>。不过，气旋内很快形成紧密的核心，贡萨洛在10月12日开始[[快速增强|快速增强]]。次日清晨，风暴中出现[[风眼|眼状特征]]，在加勒比海东部的[[安地卡岛|安地卡岛]]附近升级成一级飓风{{#tag:ref|根据[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]的定义，飓风是指持续风速在每小时119公里或以上的[[北大西洋热带气旋|大西洋]]和东北太平洋[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，这一标准和西北太平洋的台风相同<ref name="glos">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml}}</ref>。|group="注"}}。此后不久，风暴直接从该岛上空经过。<ref name="tcr" />飓风接下来吹袭[[圣马丁岛_(加勒比海)|圣马丁岛]]和[[安圭拉|安圭拉]]，从[[英属维尔京群岛|英属维尔京群岛]]以北近海掠过并继续增强<ref name="tcr" />。到了这个时候，贡萨洛已沿高压脊边缘开始朝西北方向移动<ref name="disc11">{{cite web | author = Todd B. Kimberlain | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705145846/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.011.shtml | date = 2014-10-14 | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Discussion Number 11 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.011.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-05}}</ref>。

10月14日，风眼收缩至28公里直径，在卫星图像上变得更加清晰<ref>{{cite web | author = Stacy R. Stewart | date = 2014-10-14 | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Discussion Number 10 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.010.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705150916/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.010.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-05}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}下午18点，贡萨洛在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]][[圣胡安_(波多黎各)|圣胡安]]以北约270公里洋面强化成三级飓风<ref name="tcr" />，并在6小时后成为[[2011年大西洋飓风季|2011年]]的飓风奥菲莉亚以来大西洋盆地形成的首场四级飓风。风暴内随后呈现出同心风眼墙结构，表明气旋会立即开始[[眼墙置换|眼墙置换]]，美国国家飓风中心在报告中称，贡萨洛这时的内部核心已经达到“能够达到的最小程度”<ref name="disc13">{{cite web | author = John P. Cangialosi | date = 2014-10-15 | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Discussion Number 13 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141107120803/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.013.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.013.shtml | archivedate = 2014-11-07}}</ref>。眼墙置换令风暴核心受到短时间的扰乱，飓风因此略有减弱<ref name="disc14">{{cite web | author = John P. Cangialosi | date = 2014-10-15 | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Discussion Number 14 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.014.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705124939/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.014.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-05}}</ref>，但到了10月15日晚眼墙置换完成后，系统恢复稳定并继续加强<ref>{{cite web | author = Eric S. Blake | date = 2014-10-15 | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Discussion Number 15 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | archivedate = 2015-07-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705130228/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.015.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.015.shtml}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = Michael J. Brennan | date = 2014-10-16 | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Discussion Number 16 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705150555/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.016.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-05 | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.016.shtml}}</ref>。次日清晨，正向北移动的贡萨洛达到风力时速230公里，最低[[气压|气压]]940[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.76[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。到了当天夜间，风暴已因高压脊减退而转向[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]，朝逼近美国东部上空的[[低压槽|低压槽]]前进。<ref name="tcr" />

10月16日晚至次日清晨，飓风从西南偏南方向逼近百慕大，因此经历又一轮内部波动，风暴强度也在此期间开始减弱<ref name="tcr" /><ref>{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2014-10-17 | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Discussion Number 21 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705123624/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.021.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.021.shtml | archivedate = 2015-07-05}}</ref>。飓风周围的云顶回暖，对流也变得不及之前均匀，这很可能是因为气旋行经海域水温降低，风切变增多所致<ref>{{cite web | author = Todd Kimberlain and Michael Brennan | date = 2014-10-17 | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Discussion Number 20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705131654/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.020.shtml | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | archivedate = 2015-07-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.020.shtml}}</ref>。贡萨洛在北部风眼墙穿越百慕大期间降级成二级飓风<ref>{{cite web | author = Stacy R. Stewart | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Intermediate Public Advisory Number 22A | date = 2014-10-17 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.public_a.022.shtml | archivedate = 2015-07-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705131806/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.public_a.022.shtml}}</ref>，并且环流中心也在{{lang|en|UTC}}10月18日凌晨0点30分直接从该岛上空经过，属正式[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。百慕大刚在10月12日受到飓风费伊突袭，不到一周后又遭贡萨洛袭击，这也是有纪录以来该岛首度在同一年飓风季中有两场飓风登陆<ref name="tcr" />。离开百慕大后，风暴继续消亡<ref>{{cite web | author = Chris Landsea | date = 2014-10-18 | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Discussion Number 25 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.025.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705150852/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.025.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-05}}</ref>，但又于10月18日表现出组织结构增强的迹象<ref>{{cite web | author = Stacy R. Stewart | date = 2014-10-18 | title = Hurricane Discussion Number 26 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705150616/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.026.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-05 | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.026.shtml}}</ref>。贡萨洛加速向东北方向移动，前进速度超过每小时80公里<ref>{{cite web | author = Michael J. Brennan | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Intermediate Public Advisory Number 28 | date = 2014-10-19 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705150002/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.public_a.028.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-05 | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.public_a.028.shtml}}</ref>，于10月19日从[[纽芬兰与拉布拉多|纽芬兰]][[阿瓦隆半岛|阿瓦隆半岛]]东南方向约80公里近海经过<ref name="tcr" />。虽然行经水域的[[海面温度|海面温度]]低于10 [[摄氏温标|°C]]，但风暴还是得以保持[[中心密集云区|中心密集云区]]和温暖的深层核心<ref name="disc29">{{cite web | author = Stacy R. Stewart | date = 2014-10-19 | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Discussion Number 29 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705150731/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.029.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-05 | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.discus.029.shtml}}</ref>。到了{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点，贡萨洛终于因气温低、风切变增多而在纽芬兰[[开普雷斯|开普雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Cape Race}}）东北方向约740公里洋面转变成强烈[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。温带风暴加速向东北偏东方向移动，于10月20日在[[冰岛|冰岛]]西南偏南方向水域被[[冷锋|锋面系统]]吸收。形成的天气系统于10月21日给[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]和欧洲本土部分地区带去暴风雨天气<ref name="tcr" />，之后还促使一片大型[[阻塞高气压|割离低气压]]形成<ref>{{cite web | author = National Climactic Data Center | title = 500MB Analysis – Heights/Vorticity 10/24/2014 00UTC | publisher = National Weather Service | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717143300/http://nomads.ncdc.noaa.gov/ncep-charts/hires/20141024/gfs.500.hgt.vor.nh.anl.00.20141024.gif | url = http://nomads.ncdc.noaa.gov/ncep-charts/hires/20141024/gfs.500.hgt.vor.nh.anl.00.20141024.gif | deadurl = yes | format = GIF | archivedate = 2015-07-17 }}</ref>。

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Gonzalo_Viewed_From_the_International_Space_Station.jpg|thumb]]观察逼近百慕大的飓风贡萨洛]]
贡萨洛成形时，加勒比地区东部从[[瓜德罗普|瓜德罗普]]和[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]海岸间的多个政府发布[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告]]；随着风暴逐渐增强并逼近，英属维尔京群岛、安圭拉和圣马丁岛都收到飓风警告<ref name="tcr" />。多家大型邮轮公司更改航线，以求避开风暴<ref name="twc">{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Hammers Antigua, Damages Homes and Disrupts Caribbean Cruises | date = 2014-10-14 | archivedate = 2015-06-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150610050153/http://www.weather.com/storms/hurricane/news/tropical-storm-hurricane-gonzalo-caribbean-puerto-rico-virgin-islands-travel | publisher = The Weather Channel | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.weather.com/storms/hurricane/news/tropical-storm-hurricane-gonzalo-caribbean-puerto-rico-virgin-islands-travel}}</ref>。

10月14日晚，虽然飓风尚在该岛以南1130公里洋面，但百慕大气象局还是对岛上发布了飓风观察预警，再于次日升级成飓风警告<ref name="tcr" />。岛上数天前刚经受过毁灭性异常之大的[[飓风费伊_(2014年)|飓风费伊]]摧残，面对即将来袭的贡萨洛，居民迅速开始防灾准备工作，获取紧急救援物资，加快前一场飓风的善后清理工作<ref>{{cite news | title = Category 4 Hurricane Gonzalo aims for Bermuda | date = 2014-10-15 | work = The Arizona Republic | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.azcentral.com/story/news/world/2014/10/14/hurricane-gonzalo-bermuda/17268057/}}</ref>。百慕大总理迈克尔·邓克利（{{lang|en|Michael Dunkley}}）建议居民在10月16日下午完成大部分准备工作<ref>{{cite news | author = Doyle Rice | title = 'Dangerous' Hurricane Gonzalo roars toward Bermuda | date = 2014-10-16 | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/weather/2014/10/16/hurricane-gonzalo-bermuda/17345911/}}</ref>。多家银行和商户这天停止营业<ref>{{cite news | author = Raymond Hainey | date = 2014-10-16 | title = Businesses close early and prepare for Gonzalo | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | archivedate = 2014-11-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141118165957/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/BUSINESS03/141019802 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/BUSINESS03/141019802}}</ref>，学校和政府部门则在10月17日关闭<ref>{{cite news | author = Jonathan Bell | date = 2014-10-16 | title = Are you ready? | work = The Royal Gazette | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150409234350/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141015/NEWS/141019813 | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141015/NEWS/141019813 | archivedate = 2015-04-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。只有一所学校作为风暴避难所继续开放<ref name="causeway">{{cite news | author = Jonathon Bell | title = Causeway to close 10am tomorrow | date = 2014-10-16 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150329113643/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/NEWS/141019762 | archivedate = 2015-03-29 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/NEWS/141019762}}</ref>，有66人最终前来躲避<ref>{{cite news | date = 2014-10-18 | title = Premier praises Island’s response | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150406124758/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019697 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019697 | archivedate = 2015-04-06}}</ref>。客车和渡轮服务于10月16日晚暂停<ref name="causeway" />。《皇家公报》（{{lang|en|''Royal Gazette''}}）是百慕大当时唯一的日报，但10月17日这天也没有列印，10月18日的报纸则免费发行<ref>{{cite news | date = 2014-10-16 | title = Revised print schedule | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | archivedate = 2014-11-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141118163536/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/NEWS/141019789 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/NEWS/141019789}}</ref>。岛上多地有[[百慕大团|百慕大团]]军人驻扎，为应急响应人员提供帮助，并确保公众安全<ref>{{cite news | title = Regiment in action as Gonzalo nears | date = 2014-10-16 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/NEWS/141019754 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129141823/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/NEWS/141019754 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-11-29}}</ref>。

加勒比公用事业电力服务公司派出架线工对百慕大电力照明公司提供协助，以应对贡萨洛来袭引发的停电情况。飓风费伊在岛上引发的大面积停电尚未完全恢复，百慕大电力照明公司在多个战略要点驻守车辆和物资，准备应对下一场飓风的袭击<ref>{{cite news | title = CARILEC Prepared To Send Crews To Help | date = 2014-10-15 | work = Bernews | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://bernews.com/2014/10/belco/ | archivedate = 2014-11-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141130215532/http://bernews.com/2014/10/belco/}}</ref>。10月16日清晨，百慕大电力照明公司将工作重点从恢复供电转为应对贡萨洛，岛上仍有约1500户居民家中停电，工作人员还请这些居民暂时不要打电话报告停电情况<ref>{{cite news | author = Owain Johnston-Barnes | title = Belco: 1,500 still without power | date = 2014-10-16 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | archivedate = 2014-10-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141020113439/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/NEWS/141019782 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/NEWS/141019782}}</ref>。[[英国皇家海军|英国皇家海军]]护卫舰“[[英国皇家海军阿盖尔号护卫舰|阿盖尔号]]”（{{lang|en|Argyll}}）在风暴到达前从加勒比赶到百慕大提供紧急援助<ref>{{cite news | author = Simon Jones | title = HMS Argyll heading to Bermuda | date = 2014-10-16 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/NEWS/141019763 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150715011601/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141016/NEWS/141019763 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-15}}</ref>。飓风产生的涌浪开始堆积后，公共海滩随之关闭，岛上还因预计会有长时间的狂风而于10月17日清晨开始关闭长堤<ref name="causeway" />。此外，[[百慕大国际机场|百慕大国际机场]]也在风暴来袭前关闭<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Gonzalo: Bermuda 'bruised' by direct hit | date = 2014-10-18 | work = BBC News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141204024035/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-29679079 | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-29679079 | archivedate = 2014-12-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，62架次商业航班取消。3艘原定前来百慕大的邮轮更改航线<ref name="cruise">{{cite news | author = Sarah Lagan | title = Gonzalo could have cost tourism $1m a day | date = 2014-10-23 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141204024035/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-29679079 | archivedate = 2014-12-04 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141023/NEWS/141029837 }}</ref>。

== 影响和善后 ==

=== 加勒比地区 ===
贡萨洛在达到飓风强度后不久经过小安的列斯群岛东北部，安提瓜测得持续风速为每小时124公里，阵风时速则有145公里<ref name="aab">{{cite web | author = Dale C. S. Destin | title = Antigua and Barbuda Weather Summary 2014 | date = 2015-03-30 | publisher = Antigua and Barbuda Meteorological Service | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518091144/http://www.antiguamet.com/Climate/ANNUAL_WX/NationalSummary_2014.pdf | url = http://www.antiguamet.com/Climate/ANNUAL_WX/NationalSummary_2014.pdf | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | format = PDF}}</ref>。多条道路被连根拔起的树木阻塞，包括多所学校在内的大量建筑物受到严重破坏<ref name="twc" /><ref name="aab" />。岛上电力基本中断<ref name="twc" />，还有许多船只因[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]受损{{#tag:ref|[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]指平均潮汐高度和风暴产生潮汐高度之间的差距<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}<ref name="aab" />。多所学校和商店被迫关闭，岛上为灾民开设了4个应急避难所<ref name="twc" />。[[维尔伯德国际机场|维尔伯德国际机场]]之前已经关闭以防万一，但又因瓦砾和洪灾被迫延长关闭时间<ref>{{cite news | author = Raisa Charles | title = Air and sea ports resume operations today | date = 2014-10-14 | newspaper = The Antigua Observer | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518092903/http://antiguaobserver.com/air-and-sea-ports-resume-operations-today/ | url = http://antiguaobserver.com/air-and-sea-ports-resume-operations-today/ | archivedate = 2015-05-18}}</ref>。大量民宅受到破坏，其中大部分都是屋顶受损，[[圣乔治区_(安地卡及巴布达)|圣乔治区]]的灾情最为严重<ref name="AntiguaDamage">{{cite news | author = Martina Johnson | newspaper = The Antigua Observer | date = 2014-12-16 | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | title = Homes suffered greatest Gonzalo damage, report says | archivedate = 2015-02-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150201225551/http://antiguaobserver.com/homes-suffered-greatest-gonzalo-damage-report-says/ | url = http://antiguaobserver.com/homes-suffered-greatest-gonzalo-damage-report-says/}}</ref>。乡村和各种农作物都受到严重影响<ref name="aab" />，引发飓风过后立即出现农产品短缺的担忧<ref>{{cite news | author = Theresa Gordon | title = Storm damage in agriculture sector not complete | date = 2014-10-20 | newspaper = The Antigua Observer | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023044956/http://antiguaobserver.com/storm-damage-in-agriculture-sector-not-complete/ | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://antiguaobserver.com/storm-damage-in-agriculture-sector-not-complete/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-23}}</ref>。部分种植者失去了所有香蕉作物<ref name="aab" />。

[[巴布达岛|巴布达岛]]的阵风时速为113公里<ref name="tcr" />，经雷达图像估计降雨量达到150毫米<ref name="aab" />。虽然岛上所受破坏程度不及安提瓜，但仍报告有树枝折断、洪灾及公共设施受损<ref>{{cite news | author = Kadeem Joseph | title = Barbuda spared storm damage | date = 2014-10-14 | newspaper = The Antigua Observer | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://antiguaobserver.com/barbuda-spared-storm-damage/ | archivedate = 2014-10-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141016065105/http://antiguaobserver.com/barbuda-spared-storm-damage/}}</ref>。[[安提瓜和巴布达|安提瓜和巴布达]]共因这场风暴遭受了约4000万美元损失，其中大部分属安提瓜岛上的住宅、政府建筑所受破坏和农业损失<ref name="aab" /><ref name="AntiguaDamage" />，还包括[[美国航空|美国航空]]未能在飓风来袭期间把足够数量乘客运离而承担的赔偿<ref>{{cite news | publisher = The Antigua Observer | date = 2014-10-22 | accessdate = 2015-07-17 | title = Airline reimbursements contribute to Gonzalo’s price tag | archivedate = 2015-02-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150220020450/http://antiguaobserver.com/airline-reimbursements-contribute-to-gonzalos-price-tag/ | url = http://antiguaobserver.com/airline-reimbursements-contribute-to-gonzalos-price-tag/}}</ref>。虽然有多人因风暴受轻伤，但都没有生命危险<ref>{{cite news | author = Martina Johnson | title = Hospital records multiple injuries during storm | date = 2014-10-15 | newspaper = The Antigua Observer | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518092828/http://antiguaobserver.com/hospital-records-multiple-injuries-during-storm/ | url = http://antiguaobserver.com/hospital-records-multiple-injuries-during-storm/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。更偏西部的[[圣克里斯多福与尼维斯|圣克里斯多福与尼维斯]]因飓风导致局部停电<ref name="ccrif">{{cite web | title = Tropical Cyclone Gonzalo (AL082014) | date = 2014-10-20 | publisher = The Caribbean Catastrophe Risk Insurance Facility | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518092953/http://www.ccrif.org/sites/default/files/publications/20141020_CCRIF_EventBriefing_TCGonzalo.pdf | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | deadurl = yes | format = PDF | url = http://www.ccrif.org/sites/default/files/publications/20141020_CCRIF_EventBriefing_TCGonzalo.pdf }}</ref>，降雨量总体在25至50毫米间，瓜德罗普的阵风时速约为93公里<ref>{{cite news|author=Météo-France |title=Antilles : retour sur l'ouragan Gonzalo |date=2014-10-15 |newspaper=Agence NEWS Press |accessdate=2015-07-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518103447/http://www.newspress.fr/Communique_FR_283013_2531.aspx |archivedate=2015-05-18 |url=http://www.newspress.fr/Communique_FR_283013_2531.aspx }}</ref>。
[[File:Orient_Beach_after_Hurricane_Gonzalo,_St_Martin.jpg|thumb]]

圣马丁岛周边有数十艘船因风暴失事，其中单[[辛普森湾泻湖|辛普森湾泻湖]]就有22艘，一位正在船上的老人遇难。圣马丁和[[圣巴泰勒米|圣巴泰勒米]]有两人失踪<ref name="martin">{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Hurricane Gonzalo strengthens, threatens Bermuda | date = 2014-10-14 | work = CBC News | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/hurricane-gonzalo-strengthens-threatens-bermuda-1.2797631 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141205055104/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/hurricane-gonzalo-strengthens-threatens-bermuda-1.2797631 | archivedate = 2014-12-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，并且经过数月也没有找到，推定已经死亡<ref name="tcr" />，另外14人失踪后顺利生还<ref name="week">{{cite news | author = Delphine Gavach | title = L'ouragan Gonzalo a frappé fort | date = 2014-10-21 | newspaper = St. Martin's Week | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141027181137/http://www.stmartinweek.com/rubriques/societe/l-ouragan-gonzalo-a-frappe-fort.html | url = http://www.stmartinweek.com/rubriques/societe/l-ouragan-gonzalo-a-frappe-fort.html | archivedate = 2014-10-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。圣巴泰勒米的持续风速为每小时138公里，阵风时速则达203公里<ref name="tcr" />。倒塌的树木阻塞街道，古斯塔夫三世机场跑道上的一架飞机被风刮得翻转过来<ref name="barts">{{cite web | author = Agence France-Presse | title = Hurricane Gonzalo bears down on the Bahamas | date = 2014-10-15 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/saint-barth-lemy-france/gonzalo-gathers-strength-major-hurricane | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150715010644/http://reliefweb.int/report/saint-barth-lemy-france/gonzalo-gathers-strength-major-hurricane | archivedate = 2015-07-15}}</ref>。另据报道，圣巴泰勒米有多达40艘船搁浅<ref>{{cite news | author = Agence France-Presse | title = Cyclone Gonzalo: deux personnes disparues en mer | date = 2014-10-14 | newspaper = Le Nouvel Observateur | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | archivedate = 2015-07-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150715011235/http://tempsreel.nouvelobs.com/societe/20141014.OBS1963/ouragan-gonzalo-3-personnes-disparues-a-st-barthelemy-et-st-martin.html | url = http://tempsreel.nouvelobs.com/societe/20141014.OBS1963/ouragan-gonzalo-3-personnes-disparues-a-st-barthelemy-et-st-martin.html}}</ref>。

圣马丁岛的持续风速为每小时100公里，[[埃斯佩兰斯机场|埃斯佩兰斯机场]]的测试仪器在测得时速150公里阵风后失效。岛上降雨量达145毫米<ref name="tcr" />。新闻报道显示许多民宅进水，城区被淹<ref name="kitts">{{cite news|title=French St. Martin Post Gonzalo Recovery |date=2014-10-20 |newspaper=The St. Kitts and Nevis Observer |accessdate=2015-07-18 |url=http://www.thestkittsnevisobserver.com/2014/10/17/gonzalo-recovery.html |archivedate=2015-05-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518102058/http://www.thestkittsnevisobserver.com/2014/10/17/gonzalo-recovery.html |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。荷属圣马丁各地的供水和供电受到飓风的严重影响，许多民居遭受重创。圣马丁动物园受到严重的结构性破坏，不过里面的所有动物都安然无恙<ref name="martin" />。法属圣马丁遭受的破坏程度相对较轻，只有少量屋顶和窗户受损<ref name="kitts" />，但东方海滩“已是完全毁灭的景象”，多家商店受到严重破坏<ref>{{cite news|title=Gonzalo exacts a heavy toll on boats, boat owners |date=2014-10-15 |newspaper=The Daily Herald |accessdate=2015-07-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518085215/http://thedailyherald.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=50793%3Agonzalo-exacts-a-heavy-toll-on-boats-boat-owners&catid=1%3Aislands-news&Itemid=54 |archivedate=2015-05-18 |url=http://thedailyherald.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=50793:gonzalo-exacts-a-heavy-toll-on-boats-boat-owners&catid=1:islands-news&Itemid=54 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。来自[[马提尼克|马提尼克]]的应急响应人员和军用飞机赶赴圣巴泰勒米和圣马丁协助灾后恢复工作<ref>{{cite news | author = Philippe Daniel | title = Des renforts Martiniquais après l'ouragan Gonzalo | date = 2014-10-14 | publisher = DOMactu.com | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518094513/http://www.domactu.com/actualite/141014122600184/martinique-des-renforts-martiniquais-apres-l-ouragan-gonzalo/ | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | url = http://www.domactu.com/actualite/141014122600184/martinique-des-renforts-martiniquais-apres-l-ouragan-gonzalo/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = La Martinique vient en aide aux îles du Nord suite au passage de l'ouragan Gonzalo | date = 2014-10-14 | newspaper = Sa Ka Fet Matinik | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518090220/http://www.sakafetmatinik.fr/pages/voir/actus/la-martinique-vient-en-aide-aux-iles-du-nord-suite-au-passage-de-l-ouragan-gonzalo.html | url = http://www.sakafetmatinik.fr/pages/voir/actus/la-martinique-vient-en-aide-aux-iles-du-nord-suite-au-passage-de-l-ouragan-gonzalo.html }}</ref>。

安圭拉降下暴雨，[[克莱顿·劳埃德国际机场|克莱顿·劳埃德国际机场]]和多个区的部分地区被淹，政府为此获得50万美元“过度降水”的保险赔付<ref>{{cite web | title = CCRIF to make First Payout on Excess Rainfall Policy to Anguilla after Hurricane Gonzalo Rains | date = 2014-10-27 | publisher = Caribbean Catastrophe Risk Insurance Facility | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518093005/http://www.ccrif.org/news/ccrif-make-first-payout-excess-rainfall-policy-anguilla-after-hurricane-gonzalo-rains | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.ccrif.org/news/ccrif-make-first-payout-excess-rainfall-policy-anguilla-after-hurricane-gonzalo-rains }}</ref>。该岛最东端和最西端所受冲击最为强烈，电线杆、植被和屋顶受到破坏<ref name="ccrif" />，公立学校直至10月20日或以后才陆续开放<ref name="intact">{{cite news | title = Gonzalo Pounds Anguilla; Tourism Plant Intact | date = 2014-10-18 | newspaper = The Anguillian | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-07-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717010506/http://theanguillian.com/2014/10/gonzalo-pounds-anguilla-tourism-plant-intact/ | url = http://theanguillian.com/2014/10/gonzalo-pounds-anguilla-tourism-plant-intact/}}</ref>。岛上唯一的医院也出现轻度洪灾<ref name="ccrif" />。

贡萨洛在波多黎各部分地区和[[维尔京群岛|维尔京群岛]]产生狂风天气，导致停电，并促使20人躲进应急避难所<ref>{{cite news | author = Thomas Barrabi | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Update: Bermuda Declares Hurricane Watch, Storm Could Reach Category 4 Winds | date = 2014-10-15 | work = International Business Times | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717131112/http://www.ibtimes.com/hurricane-gonzalo-update-bermuda-declares-hurricane-watch-storm-could-reach-category-4-1705297 | archivedate = 2015-07-17 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.ibtimes.com/hurricane-gonzalo-update-bermuda-declares-hurricane-watch-storm-could-reach-category-4-1705297}}</ref><ref name="fema">{{cite web | author = Federal Emergency Management Agency | title = Daily  Operations Briefing: Tuesday, October 14, 2014 | publisher = U.S. Department of Homeland Security | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717013403/https://complete-em.com/NewsFilePath/953075/63548890331000000014.pdf | url = https://complete-em.com/NewsFilePath/953075/63548890331000000014.pdf | archivedate = 2015-07-17}}</ref>。[[圣托马斯岛_(美属维尔京群岛)|圣托马斯岛]]上的[[西里尔·E·金机场|西里尔·E·金机场]]因风暴临时关闭<ref name="fema" />，机场内出现大风，阵风时速达到56公里<ref>{{cite news|author=Lynda Lohr |title=Rapid Intensification Caused Gonzalo to Veer Away |date=2014-10-14 |work=St. Croix Source |accessdate=2015-07-18 |archivedate=2015-07-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716221227/http://stcroixsource.com/content/news/local-news/2014/10/14/rapid-intensification-caused-gonzalo-veer-away |deadurl=yes |url=http://stcroixsource.com/content/news/local-news/2014/10/14/rapid-intensification-caused-gonzalo-veer-away }}</ref>。除此以外，飓风产生的恶劣海况还对[[大安的列斯群岛|大安的列斯群岛]]部分地区和[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]构成影响<ref name="pr">{{cite news | title = Category 4 Hurricane Gonzalo aims for Bermuda | date = 2014-10-15 | work = The Columbus Dispatch | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717023000/http://www.dispatch.com/content/stories/national_world/2014/10/15/major-hurricane-heads-far-from-u-s-.html | archivedate = 2015-07-17 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.dispatch.com/content/stories/national_world/2014/10/15/major-hurricane-heads-far-from-u-s-.html}}</ref>。

=== 百慕大 ===
贡萨洛来袭期间，百慕大岛上经历了持续约6小时的飓风强度狂风，以风暴后方产生的西北风力度最强<ref name="tcr" />。热带风暴强度风力则持续了24小时之久<ref name="raiv">{{cite news | author = Government of Bermuda | title = Review of the Past Hurricane Season | date = 2015-04 | agency = RA IV Hurricane Committee | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | publisher = World Meteorological Association | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | deadurl = no | format = DOC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518094118/http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/HC-37D0c424bermuda.doc | url = http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/HC-37D0c424bermuda.doc}}</ref>。高架气象站测得的风速最高，两地分别测得每小时175公里的10分钟持续风速和232公里的阵风时速；接近海平面的长堤上阵风时速也有182公里<ref name="tcr" />。岛上机场测得72毫米降水，但考虑到狂风的影响，实际降雨量有可能更大。贡萨洛的风眼经过期间，岛上云淡风轻，但也被海水产生的雾气笼罩<ref name="raiv" />。飓风来袭时正逢退潮，所以风暴潮造成的影响很小。该岛北部的埃索码头出现的风暴潮最高，比正常水位高约0.99米<ref name="tcr" /><ref name="raiv" />。
[[File:Hurricane_Gonzalo_approaching_and_passing_Bermuda.gif|thumb]]

狂风刮倒电线杆和数以百计的树木（情况很可能因之前数月创纪录的降雨量导致土壤湿软而加剧），岛上几乎没有可供通行的道路<ref name="raiv" /><ref name="blocked">{{cite news | title = Roads blocked and serious damage Island-wide | date = 2014-10-18 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2014-11-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141118164042/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019705 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019705}}</ref><ref name="species" />。多个外来树种被风暴夷平，事实证明当地原生树种更具弹性<ref name="species">{{cite news | author = Harrison EGN Isaac Sr | date = 2014-10-25 | title = Storms’ impact on our bees | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518095343/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141025/COMMENT/141029747 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141025/COMMENT/141029747 | archivedate = 2015-05-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Leanne McGrath | title = Storms have silver lining | date = 2014-11-03 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518102355/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141103/NEWS/141109953 | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141103/NEWS/141109953 | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。飓风费伊和贡萨洛过后，一堆肥处理厂平均每天收到的植物碎屑从过去的100卡车暴增至1200卡车<ref>{{cite news | author = Sarah Lagan | title = Tipping fees resumed at Marsh Folly | date = 2015-01-27 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20150126/NEWS/150129778 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518103904/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20150126/NEWS/150129778 | archivedate = 2015-05-18}}</ref>。[[百慕大国民信托|百慕大国民信托]]管理的物业共因两场风暴遭受了价值约26万美元的损失，其中包括自然保护区和墓地所受破坏<ref>{{cite news | author = Simon Jones | title = Trust lands suffered $260,000 of storm damage | date = 2014-11-07 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-03-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150327133624/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141107/NEWS/141109777 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141107/NEWS/141109777}}</ref>。由于大量植被受到破坏，百慕大植物园和树木园出于安全考虑关闭<ref>{{cite news | title = Botanical Gardens, Arboretum closed | date = 2014-10-23 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141023/NEWS/141029826 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150718090500/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141023/NEWS/141029826 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-18}}</ref>。

10月17日下午，百慕大岛上开始因天气恶化出现停电情况<ref>{{cite news | title = Midnight: 30,700 in the dark as Gonzalo resumes | date = 2014-10-18 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150331054343/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141017/NEWS/141019729 | archivedate = 2015-03-31 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141017/NEWS/141019729}}</ref>。风暴来袭期间，岛上全部3.6万电力用户中有约3.1万失去供电<ref>{{cite news | title = Belco restoration: 26,775 without power at 11.30am | date = 2014-10-18 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2014-10-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023113614/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019704 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019704}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Updating On BELCO’s Service Restoration | date = 2014-10-18 | work = Bernews | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-06-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150617183946/http://bernews.com/2014/10/regiment-soldiers-aid-gonzalo-clean/ | deadurl = no | url = http://bernews.com/2014/10/regiment-soldiers-aid-gonzalo-clean/}}</ref>，其中还包括飓风费伊过后供电尚未恢复的1500户<ref>{{cite news | author = Owain Johnston-Barnes | title = A last few ‘undetected’ Belco customers without power | date = 2014-11-01 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2014-11-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141110014536/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141101/NEWS/141109974 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141101/NEWS/141109974}}</ref>。加勒比公用事业电力服务公司后备人员对特派任务提供支援，这类任务包括恢复商业用电，以及贡萨洛来袭前就已中断的生活用电<ref>{{cite news | author = Jonathan Bell | title = Electricity restoration encounters obstacles | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150324235335/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141024/NEWS/141029771 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-03-24 | date = 2014-10-24 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141024/NEWS/141029771}}</ref>。供电要到11月3日才完全恢复<ref name="raiv" />，百慕大电力照明公司在飓风费伊和贡萨洛过后一共花费了290万美元修整供电系统，更换了228根电线杆、80个[[变压器|变压器]]，替换的输电线缆总长超过6500米<ref>{{cite news | author = Jonathan Kent | title = Belco seeks electricity price increase | date = 2015-05-12 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518092249/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20150512/BUSINESS03/150519918 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20150512/BUSINESS03/150519918 | archivedate = 2015-05-18}}</ref>。包括电视和互联网在内的其它公共服务也受到影响，技术人员到11月还在处理各种故障<ref name="raiv" />。主要街道上有约600盏路灯在飓风过后失效，其它小街道上还有数百盏，部分路灯直到2015年1月仍未恢复正常<ref>{{cite news | author = Simon Jones | title = Anger over street lighting outages | date = 2015-05-15 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518103904/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20150126/NEWS/150129778 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20150126/NEWS/150129778}}</ref>。

飓风令岛上的建筑物受到结构性破坏，有些只是表层破损，有些则是屋顶或整面墙壁倒塌，但后一种情况较为少见<ref name="raiv" />。许多建筑的屋顶受到一定程度破坏，包括多所教堂、一家游客中心、位于[[哈密尔顿_(百慕大)|哈密尔顿]]的国会大厦，以及位于[[普罗斯佩克特营|普罗斯佩克特营]]的百慕大警察总部<ref>{{cite news | author = Simon Jones | title = Church seeks help to fund roof repairs | date = 2015-02-20 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150225155936/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20150220/NEWS/150229978 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20150220/NEWS/150229978 | archivedate = 2015-02-25}}</ref><ref name="house">{{cite news | title = House of Assembly roof among damage Island-wide | date = 2014-10-18 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019699 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717000736/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019699 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-17}}</ref><ref name="reopen">{{cite news | author = Leanne McGrath | title = Causeway reopens at 1.10pm | date = 2014-10-18 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717024552/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019698 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019698 | archivedate = 2015-07-17}}</ref>。较为老旧的建筑物出现实质性破坏的情况特别多<ref name="tcr" />，建筑法规要求较低的商业存储建筑也是如此<ref name="ceo">{{cite news | author = Raymond Hainey | title = Damage costs likely to range between $50-100 million — BF&M CEO Wight | date = 2014-10-27 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518103901/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141027/BUSINESS01/141029704 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141027/BUSINESS01/141029704 | archivedate = 2015-05-18}}</ref>。2014年12月，5个新的板岩采石场获批，以满足市场对屋面材料的需求<ref>{{cite news | author = Jonathan Bell | title = Buildings still bear scars from Gonzalo | date = 2014-12-19 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141219/NEWS/141219649 | archivedate = 2014-12-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141219205437/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141219/NEWS/141219649}}</ref>。爱德华七世国王纪念医院的新旧楼房都受到破坏，导致设施暴露在外<ref>{{cite news | title = Damage to hospital roof reported | date = 2014-10-17 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2014-10-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023022404/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141017/NEWS/141019708 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141017/NEWS/141019708}}</ref>。[[百慕大水族馆，博物馆和动物园|百慕大水族馆，博物馆和动物园]]的一处景点屋顶被掀，还一度受到海岸侵蚀的威胁，不过最终并没有动物受到伤害<ref>{{cite news | title = Aquarium damaged in Gonzalo | date = 2014-10-18 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2014-10-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023171043/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019691 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141018/NEWS/141019691}}</ref>，破坏的一角一直被刮到400米外<ref name="property">{{cite web | author = Tim Sprinkle | title = Take a look at the damage that Hurricane Gonzalo left behind in Bermuda | date = 2014-10-21 | publisher = PropertyCasualty360 | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518080610/http://www.propertycasualty360.com/2014/10/21/take-a-look-at-the-damage-that-hurricane-gonzalo-l?t=catastrophe-restoration&page=7 | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | url = http://www.propertycasualty360.com/2014/10/21/take-a-look-at-the-damage-that-hurricane-gonzalo-l?t=catastrophe-restoration&page=7}}</ref>。

百慕大机场的屋顶和跑道照明设施受到一定程度破坏<ref name="airport">{{cite news | title = EMO Statement: Airport, Causeway, Schools | date = 2014-10-18 | work = Bernews | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-06-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150617221251/http://bernews.com/2014/10/emo-statement-airport-causeway-schools/ | url = http://bernews.com/2014/10/emo-statement-airport-causeway-schools/ | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Airport to reopen today | date = 2014-10-19 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717004120/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141019/NEWS/141019685 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141019/NEWS/141019685 | archivedate = 2015-07-17}}</ref>，百慕大气象局大楼的一扇风暴活门被毁，通信机房因此进水<ref name="raiv" />。吉布斯希尔灯塔下的一间餐厅严重受损，需要更换整个屋顶<ref>{{cite news | author = Sarah Lagan | title = Hurricane repairs at Gibbs Hill Lighthouse | date = 2015-03-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150714154535/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20150329/NEWS/150329711 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-07-14 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20150329/NEWS/150329711}}</ref>。长堤总体上得以幸免，路旁的防护墙受到部分损伤，经过初步修复后就于10月18日重新开放<ref name="reopen" />，但两条车道中有一条关停数天<ref name="raiv" />。许多船只被冲上岸，部分在风暴冲击下损坏或沉没<ref name="blocked" />，还有些停在造船厂的船只翻倒<ref name="property" />。据初步估算，单[[英国皇家海军造船厂_(百慕大)|皇家海军造船厂]]就遭受了100万美元的财物损失<ref name="house" />。
[[File:Royal_Navy_Type_23_Frigate_HMS_Argyll_MOD_45153839.jpg|right]]

飓风贡萨洛是[[2003年大西洋飓风季|2003年]]的[[飓负费边|飓负费边]]以来直接影响百慕大的最强飓风<ref name="tcr" />，但破坏程度还远远不及<ref name="fabian">{{cite news | author = Raymond Hainey | title = Insurers flooded with calls — but damage is not ‘Fabian-sized’ | date = 2014-10-21 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518100849/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141021/BUSINESS03/141029957 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141021/BUSINESS03/141029957 | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。灾害模拟公司估计，贡萨洛导致的保险索赔金额在2至4亿美元之间，这其中还不包括船只所受破坏<ref name="tcr" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Early Insured Loss Estimates on Hurricane Gonzalo Up to $400M | publisher = Insurance Journal | date = 2014-10-23 | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-06-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150622092012/http://www.insurancejournal.com/news/international/2014/10/23/344544.htm | url = http://www.insurancejournal.com/news/international/2014/10/23/344544.htm}}</ref>，但百慕大最大保险公司的[[首席执行官|首席执行官]]认为，实际损失数额会小得多<ref name="ceo" />。据估计，飓风费边在2014年造成的损失会有约6.5亿美元<ref name="air">{{cite news | title = Modellers estimate $200m-$400m in insured losses from Gonzalo | date = 2014-10-22 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-07-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150718142511/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141022/BUSINESS/141029866 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141022/BUSINESS/141029866}}</ref>。部分保险公司决定将费伊和贡萨洛作为单起事件处理，这样可以让两场风暴造成的损失索赔共用一个免赔额度<ref>{{cite news | author = Raymond Hainey | title = Argus, BF&M to to treat storms as one event | date = 2014-10-24 | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141024/BUSINESS03/141029793 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518102353/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141024/BUSINESS03/141029793 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-05-18 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette}}</ref>。经过初步评估，总理邓克利宣布，实际情况远远好过预期<ref>{{cite news | title = Bermuda dodges major hurricane damage | date = 2014-10-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717190236/http://www.odt.co.nz//news/world/320362/bermuda-dodges-major-hurricane-damage | archivedate = 2015-07-17 | deadurl = no | work = Otago Daily Times | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.odt.co.nz/news/world/320362/bermuda-dodges-major-hurricane-damage}}</ref>，而且百慕大也没有人员因这场风暴丧生或重伤<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Gonzalo blacks out most of Bermuda | date = 2014-10-18 | work = BBC News | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-29669226 | archivedate = 2014-12-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141210192556/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-29669226 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

飓风过去后，阿盖尔号上的一架皇家海军直升机起飞，开始空中灾害评估。百慕大团的军人立即展开清理和救灾工作<ref name="reopen" />，政府向受到影响的屋主提供[[苫布|防水布]]<ref name="airport" />。阿盖尔号上的船员一经赶到就开始与百慕大团的军人合作<ref>{{cite news | title = Regiment and Navy help clean up Island | date = 2014-10-19 | work = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141019/NEWS/141019675 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717145124/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141019/NEWS/141019675 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-17}}</ref>。约35名船员在百慕大国际机场清理跑道上的瓦砾，机场也在经过全面评估后于10月19日重新开放<ref>{{cite news | author = Sarah Lagan | title = Royal Navy rises to the challenge | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150610033429/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141021/NEWS/141029939 | archivedate = 2015-06-10 | deadurl = no | date = 2014-10-21 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20141021/NEWS/141029939}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Airport Re-Opens, Flights Now Arriving | date = 2014-10-19 | work = Bernews | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-06-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150630090050/http://bernews.com/2014/10/airport-set-re-open-5pm-sunday/ | deadurl = no | url = http://bernews.com/2014/10/airport-set-re-open-5pm-sunday/}}</ref>。到了10月21日，岛上所有的学校都已开课<ref>{{cite news | title = Bermuda "Back In Business" After Gonzalo | date = 2014-10-22 | newspaper = Bernews | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141223191805/http://bernews.com/2014/10/debdone-bermuda-back-business-hurricane-gonzalo/ | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://bernews.com/2014/10/debdone-bermuda-back-business-hurricane-gonzalo/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-12-23}}</ref>。

=== 加拿大大西洋省份 ===
10月17日，[[加拿大飓风中心|加拿大飓风中心]]向[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]][[阿瓦隆半岛|阿瓦隆半岛]]发布热带风暴观察预警，预警范围从[[阿诺德湾|阿诺德湾]]延伸到查佩尔湾（{{lang|en|Chapel's Cove}}）<ref>{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | title = Hurricane Gonzalo Forecast Advisory Number 22 | date = 2014-10-17 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.fstadv.022.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-07-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150705145814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/al08/al082014.fstadv.022.shtml | deadurl = no}}</ref>。包括[[圣约翰斯_(纽芬兰-拉布拉多)|圣约翰斯]]在内的部分社区努力清除涵洞及雨水渠中的杂物，希望能将洪水的影响尽量降低<ref>
{{cite news | author = Jonathon Parsons | title = Bonavista preparing for Gonzalo | date = 2014-10-16 | work = The Packet | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.thepacket.ca/News/Local/2014-10-16/article-3905735/Bonavista-preparing-for-Gonzalo/1 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141019172044/http://www.thepacket.ca/News/Local/2014-10-16/article-3905735/Bonavista-preparing-for-Gonzalo/1 | archive-date = 2014-10-19 | dead-url = yes }}
</ref><ref name="canada">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Gonzalo douses Newfoundland, moves offshore | date = 2014-10-19 | work = CBC News | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710080917/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/newfoundland-labrador/hurricane-gonzalo-douses-newfoundland-moves-offshore-1.2804953 | url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/newfoundland-labrador/hurricane-gonzalo-douses-newfoundland-moves-offshore-1.2804953}}</ref>。风暴的雨带在数小时里就产生多达69毫米降水<ref name="chc">{{cite web|title=Intermediate Tropical Cyclone Information Statement at 12:01 pm ADT, Sunday, 19 October, 2014 |date=2014-10-19 |publisher=Canadian Hurricane Centre |accessdate=2015-07-18 |url=http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20141019150214.Gonzalo.info.txt.en |archivedate=2015-05-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518080333/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20141019150214.Gonzalo.info.txt.en }}</ref>，[[圣约翰斯_(纽芬兰-拉布拉多)|圣约翰斯]]因此出现城区局部洪灾<ref name="canada" />。派恩角测得的阵风时速为106公里，开普雷斯也有89公里<ref>{{cite web|author=Jeff Masters |title=Gonzalo Brushes Newfoundland; Ana Drenching Hawaii |date=2014-10-19 |publisher=Weather Underground |accessdate=2015-07-18 |url=http://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=2835 |archivedate=2015-07-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716212239/http://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=2835 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[圣约翰斯国际机场|圣约翰斯国际机场]]的持续风速为每小时54公里，阵风时速74公里<ref name="chc" />。大风致使圣约翰斯约100户居民家中断电<ref name="canada" />。[[罗伦提恩海沟|罗伦提恩海沟]]的一个浮标测得的最高浪高达21米<ref name="chc" />，风暴中心东南方向的一个石油钻井平台测得的持续风速达每小时158公里<ref name="disc29" />。风暴来袭期间的天文潮汐较低，因此没有出现重大沿海洪灾，但圣约翰斯和[[阿真舍|阿真舍]]（{{lang|en|Argentia}}）都记录下0.8米高的风暴潮<ref name="chc" />。此外，飓风还给更偏西面的[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]大西洋海岸带去大浪和离岸流<ref>{{cite web | title = Canada's Top Ten Weather Stories for 2014 | date = 2015-01-29 | publisher = Environment Canada | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150107162552/http://www.ec.gc.ca/meteo-weather/default.asp?lang=En&n=C8D88613-1&offset=7&toc=show | archivedate = 2015-01-07 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://ec.gc.ca/meteo-weather/default.asp?lang=En&n=C8D88613-1&offset=7&toc=show }}</ref>。

=== 欧洲 ===
[[File:überflutetes_Elbufer_Hamburg-Rissen_-_Orkan_Gonzalo_(22.10.2014)_03.jpg|thumb]]河段沿线出现洪灾。]]

贡萨洛的残留与其它天气系统结合并发展成温带风暴，不列颠群岛普遍受到狂风吹袭，特别是爱尔兰和英国北部上空。苏格兰西部的[[奥本|奥本]]测得每小时142公里的阵风<ref name="tcr" />，其他地区的阵风时速普遍在100公里以上<ref>{{cite web | title = Top UK wind speeds as Gonzalo’s remnants felt | date = 2014-10-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717033058/http://blog.metoffice.gov.uk/2014/10/21/top-uk-wind-speeds-as-gonzalos-remnants-felt/ | publisher = Met Office | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-07-17 | url = http://blog.metoffice.gov.uk/2014/10/21/top-uk-wind-speeds-as-gonzalos-remnants-felt/}}</ref>。系统还令不列颠各地交通受到严重干扰，[[伦敦希斯路机场|伦敦希斯路机场]]有上百架次航班被迫取消，许多渡轮推迟航程，多条公路和铁路被瓦砾阻断<ref name="tcr" />。[[海德公园|海德公园]]附近一位女性被倒塌的树木砸死，另有多人受伤<ref name="dm">{{cite news | author = Chris Pleasance and Gemma Mullin | title = Three people killed and another five injured including two children as Hurricane Gonzalo batters Britain with 108mph winds and rain | date = 2014-10-21 | newspaper = The Daily Mail | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2801196/hurricane-gonzalo-hits-75mph-winds-bringing-travel-chaos-uk-heathrow-cancels-10-flights.html | archivedate = 2014-12-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141219020656/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2801196/hurricane-gonzalo-hits-75mph-winds-bringing-travel-chaos-uk-heathrow-cancels-10-flights.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = UK severe weather: Woman dies and others injured in high winds | date = 2014-10-21 | newspaper = BBC News | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-29700594 | archivedate = 2015-04-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150418141216/http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-29700594}}</ref>。[[埃塞克斯郡|埃塞克斯郡]]一名男子正在[[千斤顶|汽车千斤顶]]撑起的面包车下修理，但狂风刮倒了千斤顶，导致该男子被车压死<ref name="tele">{{cite news | author = Tom Brooks-Pollock | title = Hurricane Gonzalo: as it happened | date = 2014-10-21 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/weather/11176145/Hurricane-Gonzalo-live-updates-as-strong-winds-batter-Britain.html | newspaper = The Telegraph | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | archivedate = 2015-07-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150702122644/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/weather/11176145/Hurricane-Gonzalo-live-updates-as-strong-winds-batter-Britain.html}}</ref>，恶劣的天气还引发交通事故，[[利物浦|利物浦]]一名男性司机因此丧生<ref name="dm" />。苏格兰和威尔士因风暴出现局部停电<ref>{{cite web | author = Eric Zerkel | title = Gonzalo's Remnants Hit the United Kingdom: 2 Killed, Travel Disrupted | date = 2014-10-22 | publisher = The Weather Channel | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150717034507/http://www.weather.com/news/news/gonzalo-united-kingdom-travel-20141021 | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.weather.com/news/news/gonzalo-united-kingdom-travel-20141021 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-17}}</ref>，相比之下，爱尔兰西北部经过时速115公里的阵风袭击后有更大范围地区停电<ref>{{cite news | title = Commuters affected as high winds hit rail and roads | date = 2014-10-21 | newspaper = The Irish Times | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/commuters-affected-as-high-winds-hit-rail-and-roads-1.1971183}}</ref>。

西欧和中欧同样受到破坏性的大风和暴雨影响，德国高海拔地区出现时速超过145公里的阵风<ref>{{cite news | title = ex-GONZALO: erste Sturm-Nachlese | date = 2014-10-22 | publisher = Wetter24 | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.wetter24.de/wetter-news/news/ch/9ad10aaca6bc89a9126a522458677a43/article/ex_gonzalo_erste_sturm_nachlese.html | archivedate = 2014-10-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141024111634/http://www.wetter24.de/wetter-news/news/ch/9ad10aaca6bc89a9126a522458677a43/article/ex_gonzalo_erste_sturm_nachlese.html}}</ref>。单[[斯图加特|斯图加特]]就有50辆汽车被掉落的瓦砾砸伤<ref name="germany">{{cite web | title = Ex-Hurrikan "Gonzalo" | date = 2014-10-24 | publisher = Institut für Meteorologie und Klimaforschung | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://www.wettergefahren-fruehwarnung.de/Ereignis/20141024_e.html}}</ref>，德国各地树木倒塌、屋顶撕裂和停电的情况非常普遍<ref>{{cite news|title=Gonzalo zieht über Bayern hinweg |date=2014-10-22 |url=http://www.br.de/nachrichten/unwetter-bayern-gewitter-104.html |accessdate=2015-07-18 |publisher=Bayerischer Rundfunk |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150809200422/http://www.br.de/nachrichten/unwetter-bayern-gewitter-104.html |archivedate=2015-08-09 }}</ref>。[[巴伐利亚州|巴伐利亚州]]首府[[慕尼黑|慕尼黑]]有一块面积超过80平方米的大铁皮屋顶被毁，部分屋顶还对地面的汽车和围栏构成破坏，估计单因这起事故就造成约50万[[欧元|欧元]]损失<ref>{{cite news | title = "Gonzalo" bringt Chaos und Schnee | date = 2014-10-22 | newspaper = Süddeutsche Zeitung | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150520152151/http://www.sueddeutsche.de/bayern/unwetter-in-bayern-gonzalo-bringt-chaos-und-schnee-1.2185232 | archivedate = 2015-05-20 | url = http://www.sueddeutsche.de/bayern/unwetter-in-bayern-gonzalo-bringt-chaos-und-schnee-1.2185232}}</ref>。整个德国共因这场风暴遭受了6000万至1亿欧元的保险损失。303号联邦公路位于[[拜罗伊特县|拜罗伊特县]]境内路段因道路湿滑引发交通事故，造成一位女性遇难<ref>{{cite news | author = Reuters | title = Experten: Sturm 'Gonzalo' kostet Versicherer auch in Europa viele Millionen | date = 2014-10-24 | archivedate = 2015-05-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150520211924/http://www.boerse-online.de/nachrichten/aktien/Experten-Sturm-Gonzalo-kostet-Versicherer-auch-in-Europa-viele-Millionen-1000344523 | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | publisher = Börse Online | url = http://www.boerse-online.de/nachrichten/aktien/Experten-Sturm-Gonzalo-kostet-Versicherer-auch-in-Europa-viele-Millionen-1000344523}}</ref>。从西北方向吹来的大风在德国北部海岸沿线产生风暴潮<ref>{{cite news | title = Leichte Sturmflut an der Nordsee | date = 2014-10-21 | publisher = Wetteronline | accessdate = 2015-07-19 | url = http://www.wetteronline.de/wetternews/2014-10-21-st | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141024022808/http://www.wetteronline.de/wetternews/2014-10-21-st | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-24}}</ref>，[[易北河|易北河]]位于[[汉堡|汉堡]]境内河段的潮水比正常水平要高2米。邻国奥地利和瑞士同样出现烈风和停电<ref name="germany" />。奥地利的[[恩卡赫河畔诺伊基兴|恩卡赫河畔诺伊基兴]]附近有[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]着陆，导致多间房屋和农场受损<ref>{{cite web|title=Wirbelsturm zerstört zahlreiche Dächer |date=2014-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521061857/http://www.ff-neukirchen.com/site/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=355%3Awirbelsturm-zerstoert-zahlreiche-daecher&catid=93%3Aeinsaetze&Itemid=115 |publisher=Freiwillige Feuerwehr Neukirchen a. d. Enknach |accessdate=2015-07-19 |archivedate=2015-05-21 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.ff-neukirchen.com/site/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=355:wirbelsturm-zerstoert-zahlreiche-daecher&catid=93:einsaetze&Itemid=115 }}</ref>。瑞士南部的阵风时速高达185公里，多条公路和铁路因此封闭<ref>{{cite news | date = 2014-10-22 | title = Les vents violents de la tempête Gonzalo ont balayé la Suisse | newspaper = Radio Télévision Suisse | accessdate = 2015-07-19 | url = http://www.rts.ch/info/suisse/6242382-les-vents-violents-de-la-tempete-gonzalo-ont-balaye-la-suisse.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141130031726/http://www.rts.ch/info/suisse/6242382-les-vents-violents-de-la-tempete-gonzalo-ont-balaye-la-suisse.html | archivedate = 2014-11-30 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。除此以外，系统还在法国南部引发[[密史脱拉风|密史脱拉风]]<ref name="germany" />。

飓风残留同上层低气压关联，给[[阿尔卑斯山|阿尔卑斯山]]部分地区带去累积有数英尺深的大雪<ref name="germany" />，之后还于10月24至25日促使[[巴尔干半岛|巴尔干半岛]]降下倾盆大雨。[[保加利亚|保加利亚]]东南部的累计降雨量估计有150毫米，产生的洪水令多个村庄完全被淹，迫使数以百计的居民撤离，还有大范围地区断水断电。[[布爾加斯|布爾加斯]]有一位女性溺亡。希腊首都[[雅典|雅典]]有多条街道被洪水淹没，冲走了数百辆汽车<ref>{{cite web | title = Ex-Hurrikan "Gonzalo" | date = 2014-10-27 | publisher = Institut für Meteorologie und Klimaforschung | accessdate = 2015-07-19 | archivedate = 2015-05-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150519093726/http://www.wettergefahren-fruehwarnung.de/Ereignis/20141027_e.html | url = http://www.wettergefahren-fruehwarnung.de/Ereignis/20141027_e.html | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Agence France-Presse | title = Greece hit by heavy flooding | date = 2014-10-25 | newspaper = Yahoo! News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150520230912/http://news.yahoo.com/greece-hit-heavy-flooding-185138807.html | accessdate = 2015-07-18 | url = http://news.yahoo.com/greece-hit-heavy-flooding-185138807.html | archivedate = 2015-05-20 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。此外，[[阿提卡|阿提卡]]地区还有超过300幢建筑物被淹<ref>{{cite news | title = Χάος από τη νεροποντή στην Αθήνα | date = 2015-10-24 | url = http://www.voria.gr/article/xaos-apo-ti-neroponti-stin-athina-vid-foto | accessdate = 2015-07-19 | publisher = Voria.gr | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150718164414/http://www.voria.gr/article/xaos-apo-ti-neroponti-stin-athina-vid-foto | archivedate = 2015-07-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

